img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3870,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/last-ayat-surah-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4951,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Last two verses of al-Baqarah sufficient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites the last two verses of Surat al-Baqarah in the night, it is enough for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 807 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/not-say-deliberately-forgot-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":4951,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Do not say I deliberately forgot the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWretched is one who says: I have forgotten such a verse. Rather, he was made to forget it. Strive to remember the Quran, for it is quicker to escape the hearts of men than camels.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/hifz-review-quran-or-forget\/","url_meta":{"origin":4951,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Memorization: Review the Quran, it can be forgotten quickly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe committed to the Quran. By the One in whose hand is my soul, it can leave you faster than a camel from its reins.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5033, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 791 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17030,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/recite-quran-regularly\/","url_meta":{"origin":4951,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Recite the Quran regularly, or you will forget","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the parable of the companion of the Quran is that of a tied camel. If he is committed to it, he will keep it. If he releases it, he will lose it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17034,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/reminded-me-of-ayat\/","url_meta":{"origin":4951,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Allah have mercy on one who reminded me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was listening to a man recite the Quran in the mosque and he said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy upon him. He reminded me of a verse I was made to forget.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 788 Grade: Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4951","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4951"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4951\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4951"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4951"},{"taxonomy":"p